name: oplog
description: A generic oplog/replication system for microservices

name: system-design
description: 深入浅出学习限流算法、数据库分库分表、分布式锁、分布式事务、云原生等Java企业级解决方案

name: MicroServicesProject
description: A beginner-friendly microservices-based e-commerce project using Spring Boot, Java, MongoDB, MySQL, Kafka, and Spring Cloud. It demonstrates building scalable, distributed systems with REST APIs, event-driven architecture, and containerization. Ideal for learning modern backend development with real-world technologies.

name: scalable-microservice
description: Welcome to the Scalable Microservice Design project. This microservice is an educational project to help developers on your first challenge designing a system to handle API requests for data storage and retrieval with high performance and scalability. The service is built using Python FastAPI and utilizes MongoDB for data persistence.

name: Containerized-Microservices-System
description: Containerized platform where users can securely upload and stream videos.

name: microservice-go
description: Order Management System with microservices in Go

name: Event-Management-System
description: A microservice-based web application that allows users to create events and manage them the way they want.

name: fast-cicd
description: A better CICD Framework。Automated deployment of microservice systems

name: e-commerce-microservices
description: The project is a microservice-based application for an e-commerce platform, focusing on order processing and inventory management. This service will handle order placement, payment processing, inventory updates, and shipment coordination in a distributed system.

name: Currency-Conversion-and-Exchange-System
description: This project used to do the conversion of USD to INR, AUD to INR, EUR to INR and vice versa.  utitlizes microservice features like Feign, Eureka server, Resilience4j, spring cloud gateway.

name: shopping-service
description: This project demonstrates a simple microservices architecture using two main services: Inventory and Shopping. It was developed to gain a deeper understanding of how microservices interact with each other in a distributed system. This Repo is dedicated to Shopping Service.

name: BykeMonitor
description: A system for monitoring checkin, checkout works in the motorbike parking areas. Using Microservices Architecture collabrating with Clean Architecture, Vertical Slice Architecture, DDD, CQRS, Replication, Sharding, Indexing, ACID Transactions, Bulk Read/Write, Caching, Message Queue, multiple Design Patterns for OOP and System Design.

name: CommentSense
description: CommentSense is an intelligent comment categorization system designed with a microservice architecture. It provides a scalable, efficient way to process and analyze large volumes of feedback, making it easier to extract valuable insights.

name: Serverless-Task-Management-Platform
description: A serverless task management platform built with AWS Lambda and microservices. Features include task creation, nested to-do lists, progress tracking, streak management, time tracking, Google Calendar integration, notifications, file attachments, and a reward system for productivity. Efficient and scalable!

name: GlobeXChange
description: A comprehensive microservices-based system for currency exchange and conversion, utilizing Spring Boot and Spring Cloud technologies. This project includes API Gateway, Eureka for service discovery, and Resilience4j for fault tolerance, with integrated metrics and tracing using Micrometer and OpenTelemetry.
